		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_COAL_PLANT_HELP">
			<Text>Each source of [ICON_RES_COAL] Coal worked by this City produces +1 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production. Requires 1 [ICON_RES_COAL] Coal. The City can only have 1 main Power Plant in it at a time.</Text>
