		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_COAL_PLANT_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Coal Plant is a Industrial era building which greatly boosts [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production of the City. It also gives bonus [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production for each source of [ICON_RES_COAL] Coal worked by the City. It requires a Factory in the City to be built and consumes 1 [ICON_RES_COAL] Coal. The City can only have 1 main Power Plant in it at a time.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_COAL_PLANT_PEDIA">
			<Text>Coal fuel power stations burn coal to produce electricity. Central Coal power plants are designed on a large scale for continuous operation. In many countries, such plants provide most of the electrical energy used. Coal power stations have rotating machinery to convert the heat energy of combustion into mechanical energy, which then operates an electrical generator.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]--Wikipedia</Text>
